@startuml Checkout_Payment
title Checkout & Payment Flow

actor "Customer" as User
participant "Storefront\n(Next.js)" as UI
participant "Order Service\n(Spring Boot)" as OS
participant "Product DB\n(PostgreSQL)" as DB
participant "Paymob API" as Paymob
participant "Notification Service" as Notify

== Load Checkout Page ==

User -> UI : Click "Proceed to Checkout"
UI -> OS : GET /cart/{storeId}\n+ Bearer Token
OS -> DB : Validate cart items\n(availability, stock, prices)
DB --> OS : Return validated cart

OS -> DB : Fetch merchant-enabled\npayment methods
DB --> OS : {COD, Paymob, FlowMerce Wallet}\n(based on merchant config)

OS --> UI : Cart summary + order total\n+ available payment methods
UI --> User : Show checkout page

== Fill Checkout Details ==

User -> UI : Enter shipping address
User -> UI : Select payment method\n(COD / Paymob / FlowMerce Wallet)

== Place Order ==

note over UI, OS
  All payment methods go through a single call.
  Stock reservation, order creation, and payment
  initiation happen atomically inside Order Service.
end note

UI -> OS : POST /orders/place\n{cartId, shippingAddress, paymentMethod}
OS -> DB : Reserve stock for all cart items
OS -> DB : Create order\n{status: PENDING}

alt Payment Method = Cash on Delivery
    OS --> UI : 200 OK {orderId}
    UI --> User : Order placed\n"Awaiting merchant confirmation"
    OS -> Notify : Notify Customer\n"Order received, pending confirmation"
    OS -> Notify : Notify Merchant\n"New COD order"

else Payment Method = Paymob
    OS -> Paymob : Create payment intention\n{amount, currency, orderId}
    Paymob --> OS : Payment key + iframe URL
    OS --> UI : Return iframe URL
    UI --> User : Show Paymob payment iframe

    User -> Paymob : Enter card details & confirm
    Paymob -> OS : Webhook: payment event\n{orderId, status}

    alt Payment Success
        OS -> DB : Update order\n{status: CONFIRMED}
        OS -> DB : Deduct reserved stock
        OS --> UI : Payment confirmed
        UI --> User : Show order confirmation page
        OS -> Notify : Notify Customer "Payment successful"
        OS -> Notify : Notify Merchant "New paid order"

    else Payment Failed
        OS -> DB : Update order\n{status: CANCELLED}
        OS -> DB : Release reserved stock
        OS --> UI : Payment failed
        UI --> User : Show error\n"Payment failed, please try again"
    end

else Payment Method = FlowMerce Wallet
    OS -> DB : Check & deduct wallet balance
    OS -> DB : Update order\n{status: CONFIRMED}
    OS -> DB : Deduct reserved stock
    OS --> UI : 200 OK {orderId}
    UI --> User : Show order confirmation page
    OS -> Notify : Notify Customer "Payment successful"
    OS -> Notify : Notify Merchant "New paid order"
end

== Merchant Confirms COD (COD only) ==

note over OS, DB
  Separate flow triggered when merchant confirms COD order
end note

OS -> DB : Update order\n{status: CONFIRMED}
OS -> DB : Deduct reserved stock
OS -> Notify : Notify Customer "Order confirmed by merchant"

@enduml